How about if there were several lists eg. separate ones for odd/even
kernels and even split pre-patches/whole releases ?  It'd save me
(and probably a fair few others) having to check for new kernels every....
well, however often.  Also that way people just interested in just the
stable whole number releases could just receive the small number of mails
they require.
